Here&#39;s the bug I created to make note of the issue and the fix:
   [ 1379208 ] crawl report/hosts-report stats leave out robots.txt
   https://sourceforge.net/tracker/index.php?func=detail&aid=1379208&group_id=73833&atid=539099

